We need not go and conſult Oracles, nor ſay who ſhall aſcend into Heaven to fetch us a reſolution from thence;
                     Deut. 30.14. Rom. 10.6, 7, 8. for as Moſes and S. Paul both ſay the Word is nigh us, even in our own hearts, there the great lines of


duty are written legibly and plainly, and an honeſt (though meanly inſtructed) mind will quickly attain the knowledge of them.
